            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_16gc' title='Col. 16GC &mdash; HL Deb 13 January 2003 vol 643 c16GC' name='column_16gc' href='#column_16gc' rel='bookmark'>16GC</a>
            understand the reasons for that: as it is a more complicated and lengthy process, it would usually be done only when the requesting authority has specifically requested it. I shall reflect on the other points and, unless there is further advice, come back to the noble Lord, Lord Carlisle, on them.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0643P0-00930'>
        <a name='S5LV0643P0_20030113_GCR_61'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-joyce-anelay' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
