          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0643P0-01144'>
        <a name='S5LV0643P0_20030113_GCR_275'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-mark-carlisle' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030113_GCR_275' title='Link to this speech by Mr Mark Carlisle' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
