        Clause 10 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0643P0-01157'>
        <a name='S5LV0643P0_20030113_GCR_288'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-bassam' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030113_GCR_288' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Bassam' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-bassam" title="Mr John Bassam">Lord Bassam of Brighton</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
